					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">unregistered wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">it appears to go eight pixels and then is reset to zero</div>
<br />
<br />Sounds to me like you are writing $00 to $2006, which resets the scroll. The only part of the scroll that isn't reset by this is the fine X scroll, which could be why you are able to scroll ~8 pixels. Make sure that the writes to $2005 are the last PPU operation of your VBlank handler.</div>

