						<div class="postbody">It seems you are updating the scroll and then updating other things, while it should be the other way around. Setting the scroll should ALWAYS be the very last thing in your VBlank handler. Any PPU operation involving $2006/$2007 messes with the VRAM address, which fucks up the scroll.</div>

